text:
They have a team of makeup artists on tap, but the Kardashian sisters are just as comfortable without makeup as they are rocking a full-on, red carpet beauty look. Yup, from Kylie Jenner to Kim Kardashian, these are the sisters' best no makeup moments (vs. some of their dreamiest glam get ups).

So, if you've ever wondered what the famous sisters look like bare-faced, spoiler: it's just as gorgeous - and we have the pictures to prove it...
authors: Vic Is The Digital Beauty Director Here At Cosmopolitan.Com Uk.
